Jmeter is used for performance testing.

Performance testing is atype of testing to ensure software application will perform well under the particular workload.

In Jmeter testing can be done by following ways

1. Record and Play:
  For this option to work, we need to configure both the Jmeter and Browser initially.

  a. Jmeter Configuration
    We need to add/set up the HTTP(S) Test Script Recorder as below.
    https://github.com/Mohsina-P/Jmeter/blob/38831b9fb7a52a0c86b12f0234127da1bd558e7d/JmeterRecordNPlaySetup.png
